==English==

===Etymology===
[[un-]] + present participle of [[stint]]

===Pronunciation===
(US) IPA: /ʌnˈstɪntɪŋ/
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪntɪŋ|-ɪntɪŋ]]

===Adjective===
'''unstinting'''
# [[generous]] and [[tireless]] with one's [[contribution]]s of time, money, etc.
#:''We thank her for her '''unstinting''' support of our new hospital.''

